
Usage:

1) build rootfs
sudo ./build_img.sh

2) build kernel 
use your command to build your own kernel
OR
Use official ubuntu kernel

3) start kvm 
   sudo ./start.sh ./rootfs.img /boot/vmlinuz-3.13.0-52-generic

4) to ssh with pwd: beammeUP
   ssh 127.0.0.1 -p 4444 -l root 

5) stop kvm
   C-A x
   


